      <section eId="sec_275_45">
        <num>275.45</num>
        <heading>Limitations of application</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_275_45__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>any broadcaster who, in connection with or as part of a radio,\ntelevision, or cable broadcast transmission, or for the purpose of\narchival preservation, transfers any such recorded sounds or images; or\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_275_45__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>any person who transfers such sounds or images for personal use,\nand without profit for such transfer.\n  2. This article shall neither enlarge nor diminish the rights of\nparties in civil litigation.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
